graph TD
    START((User Message)) --> ENTRY[entry_node<br/>Zero LLM calls<br/>- Conversation windowing<br/>- DeFi state lookup<br/>- Message building]

    ENTRY --> SEM[semantic_router_node<br/>Embedding-based classification<br/>Cosine similarity vs exemplars]

    SEM -->|"confidence >= 0.78"| ROUTE{Route to Agent}
    SEM -->|"confidence < 0.78<br/>but >= 0.50"| LLM[llm_router_node<br/>LLM confirmation]
    SEM -->|"confidence < 0.50"| GEN[default_agent]

    LLM --> ROUTE

    ROUTE -->|SWAP| SWAP[swap_agent<br/>Token swap intent collection]
    ROUTE -->|LENDING| LEND[lending_agent<br/>Supply/borrow operations]
    ROUTE -->|STAKING| STAKE[staking_agent<br/>Lido staking]
    ROUTE -->|DCA| DCA[dca_agent<br/>Recurring buy strategies]
    ROUTE -->|EXECUTION| EXEC[execution_agent NEW<br/>Aerodrome on-chain ops]
    ROUTE -->|MARKET_DATA| CRYPTO[crypto_data_agent<br/>Price, TVL, market data]
    ROUTE -->|PORTFOLIO| PORT[portfolio_advisor<br/>Portfolio analysis]
    ROUTE -->|SEARCH| SEARCH[search_agent<br/>Web search]
    ROUTE -->|GENERAL| GEN

    SWAP & LEND & STAKE & DCA & EXEC & CRYPTO & PORT & SEARCH & GEN --> FMT[formatter_node<br/>Mode-aware output formatting<br/>Fast mode vs Reasoning mode]

    FMT --> END((Response to User))

